    <entry>
      <title>hexo+github搭建博客</title>
      <link href="/2022/09/13/hexo-github-da-jian-bo-ke/"/>
      <url>/2022/09/13/hexo-github-da-jian-bo-ke/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Hexo-GitHub博客搭建"><a href="#Hexo-GitHub博客搭建" class="headerlink" title="Hexo+GitHub博客搭建"></a>Hexo+GitHub博客搭建</h2><h3 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h3><p> <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1aV411p7Bc/?spm_id_from=333.788&vd_source=729cf6d80ca215d21822e34f9c4fb599">b站博客搭建详细讲解视频</a></p><ol><li>node.js   <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_42006801/article/details/124830995"> Node.js安装与配置（详细步骤）_liyitongxue的博客-CSDN博客_nodejs配置</a></li><li>Git <a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/xueweisuoyong/p/11914045.html">Windows系统Git安装教程（详解Git安装过程） - 学为所用 - 博客园 (cnblogs.com)</a></li><li>编辑软件VScode</li><li>GitHub账号 <a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a><ul><li>github访问加速：<a href="https://pan.quark.cn/s/4c170f5763d2">https://pan.quark.cn/s/4c170f5763d2</a> 提取码：sFNj</li><li>在github新建一个仓库</li></ul></li></ol><p><img src="https://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/image-20220910114147590.png" alt="image-20220910114147590"></p><p>仓库名设置为<strong>xxx.github.io</strong>, 后面必须是<strong>github.io</strong></p><p><img src="https://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/1.png" alt="1"></p><h3 id="Hexo安装部署"><a href="#Hexo安装部署" class="headerlink" title="Hexo安装部署"></a>Hexo安装部署</h3><ol><li>Hexo安装</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">npm install hexo -g<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="2"><li>初始化博客</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo init [博客文件]<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="3"><li>安装依赖</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">npm install<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><ol start="4"><li>预览 （现在可以在本地看看博客模板）</li></ol><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo serve<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>注意：</strong>终端位置需切换到blog目录下</p><img src="http://xingqiu-tuchuang-1256524210.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/8770/2.png" alt="2"  />]]></content>
      
      
      
